Remember that it is harmless to the child and the next day it will not be able to remember anything that happened.
Useful advices
Don't wake it up.
This is useless, because the child is unconscious, so you will take it out of sleep.
Although the child speaks, it sleeps, so it rests.
Remember, if it turns out to be anxious after a couple of appearances, it is recommended to get advice or find out what reason the child has for the anxiety.
